             depos'd, That he bought the Mare of the Prisoner for 4 l. 16 s. the Thursday after last Midsummer Day, and that since the Prosecutor came and owned the Mare, and threatning to Prosecute him, he delivered it by the Advice of a Magistrate.</p>
